\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/The_Ayo_%28Olopon%29_game.jpg/180px-The_Ayo_%28Olopon%29_game.jpg\" alt=\"Ayoayo image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2</td>\n<td align=\"right\">8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">15-30m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2022-10-01T15:25:24.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"unixorn/awesome-zsh-plugins","categoryHTML":"<h2>Plugins</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/victoria-riley-barnett/Communism/\">communism</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/victoria-riley-barnett/Communism/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1,\"repo\":\"victoria-riley-barnett/Communism\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Displays a Marx quote of the day.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-10-01T14:31:07.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jthegedus/awesome-firebase","categoryHTML":"<h2>Web</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>🔧 <a href=\"https://github.com/tylim88/FirelordJS\">FirelordJS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tylim88/FirelordJS\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4